1
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:03,000
Concert.

2
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:05,560
A lot of people will be watching, right?

3
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:07,020
Hmm

4
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:10,480
The mask —

5
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,760
it's time to take it off.

6
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,040
Xiao Yao,

7
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:01,800
let's cancel this performance.

8
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,600
I'll talk to Wei Tiantian.

9
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,920
I'll also deal with those scumbags.

10
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,160
You just stay safely by my side.

11
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,160
I don't want you to suffer any more harm.

12
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,160
With you here,

13
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,240
I truly feel at ease.

14
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,160
So I want to give it a try.

15
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,960
Maybe

16
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,800
I can do it.

17
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:25,880
Xiao Yao,

18
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:26,600
do you

19
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,440
know what you're about to go through?

20
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,040
What?

21
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,360
Malicious speculation,

22
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:34,560
sordid interpretations,

23
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,000
and secondary trauma.

24
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,200
Are you really ready?

25
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,960
I'm truly very lucky

26
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,680
because I have you.

27
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:49,760
And precisely because I have all this,

28
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,120
so

29
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,720
I want to turn it into courage to face the future.

30
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,920
I also want to tell

31
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,240
the children going through darkness:

32
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,400
they will meet good people,

33
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,480
they will hear good songs,

34
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,760
they can stand up again.

35
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,400
Xiao Yao, you are truly brave.

36
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,560
I am really proud of you.

37
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,440
What?

38
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,400
You... you want me to do what?

39
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,640
I want you to be Li Xingyao's agent,

40
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,400
responsible for all her external business

41
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,600
and public image.

42
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:47,960
Why ask me?

43
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,440
You clearly

44
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,040
have more professional candidates.

45
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,160
I don't need the most professional person.

46
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,160
I need the person who cares most about Xiao Yao.

47
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,560
I already

48
00:03:58,920 --> 00:03:59,880
don't have the right

49
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,000
to stand in front of Xingyao anymore.

50
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,560
Xiao Yao won't blame you.

51
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,120
Because aside from me,

52
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,680
you are the only one who has truly been protecting her,

53
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,680
just like me,

54
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,880
hoping that he can stand in the light again.

55
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,040
Will he

56
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,320
really forgive me?

57
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,640
Xiao Yao's kindness and tolerance toward human nature —

58
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,240
that is her most precious quality.

59
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,520
But precisely because of that,

60
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,680
her future path will be harder.

61
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,080
Since he has decided to face it bravely,

62
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:34,920
I hope you can help Xiao Yao together with me.

63
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,520
You —

64
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,320
you know I like her —

65
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,760
you don't mind?

66
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,000
I mind.

67
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,960
But I care more about Xiao Yao's feelings.

68
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,840
I know

69
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,680
that you are her most valued friend

70
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,680
and her most trusted family.

71
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,960
I know how important you are to her.

72
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,760
So I cannot, because of my appearance,

73
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:01,600
let her lose a family member like you.

74
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,040
I've protected her for more than ten years,

75
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,760
yet I've always

76
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,920
stood outside the door of her world.

77
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:16,160
Because her heart has long had no room for anyone else.

78
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,200
Now I understand:

79
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,200
that person

80
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,880
must be you.

81
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,920
Alright.

82
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,680
I promise you.

83
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,040
This is not only for her;

84
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,960
it's also for myself.

85
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,560
That experience with her

86
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,920
is our shared scar.

87
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:39,320
Maybe helping her stand back in the light

88
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,000
can also help me walk out of that darkness.

89
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,560
Thank you.

90
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,120
Once again, thank you to all

91
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,400
the friends watching in the live stream

92
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,520
and those below the stage, for coming to my

93
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,320
first live stream concert.

94
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,080
Thank you.

95
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,120
last song,

96
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,920
I want to give everyone a new song,

97
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:48,680
originally written by a very talented singer.

98
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,560
The name is

99
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,640
"I Call Myself."

100
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,380
Today is the official live stream.

101
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,500
Why is he still wearing a mask?

102
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,620
Didn't you say you handled it?

103
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:36,620
Today,

104
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:38,180
I want to tell my story

105
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:40,700
right here.

106
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:44,180
Probably starting from age seven,

107
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,380
I learned one thing:

108
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,580
to hide myself.

109
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:52,260
How to make myself unnoticeable —

110
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,180
because only then

111
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:57,060
would the hurtful words and fists

112
00:08:57,620 --> 00:09:00,260
find you more slowly.

113
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:07,100
But later I realized

114
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:10,700
that escape only brings more

115
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:12,780
bullying,

116
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:14,900
scolding,

117
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,380
even humiliation.

118
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,420
Scars don't need to be hidden,

119
00:09:20,340 --> 00:09:21,140
because

120
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,540
they prove that you

121
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:28,100
once survived so bravely.

122
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:31,980
Standing here today

123
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,820
is also to tell

124
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:36,060
every one of us watching this video:

125
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:37,300
Look —

126
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:40,860
even I can live in the light.

127
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,580
Then your light

128
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:46,540
must also be on its way.

129
00:09:47,340 --> 00:09:48,380
Please be sure

130
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:50,220
to wait for it.

131
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,380
Lao Zhou, let me tell you something.

132
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:06,020
Xingyao Li, could I have an interview with you?

133
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,220
It's blowing up, look

134
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,380
Since he took off his mask.

135
00:10:08,380 --> 00:10:10,380
the number of people in the live stream has shot up.

136
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:12,860
All the trending topics are ours now.

137
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,140
Holy crap, awesome.

138
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:14,660
That's awesome

139
00:10:14,940 --> 00:10:15,540
It's solid.

140
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:16,340
Zhou, you were right.

141
00:10:16,340 --> 00:10:17,700
this time it's really solid.

142
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,860
Regarding the rumors online,

143
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:20,260
do you have anything you want to say?

144
00:10:20,460 --> 00:10:22,060
Is what Wang Daqiang said true?

145
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:24,260
Previously, there were rumors that you and this concert's

146
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:26,340
music director Mr. Zhou Jing'an were seen together,

147
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,420
having a very close relationship,

148
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:29,040
often photographed coming and going together many times.

149
00:10:29,220 --> 00:10:30,060
What exactly is your relationship?

150
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:49,980
Everyone, good work.

151
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:52,860
Today's concert by Xingyao ends here.

152
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:54,380
If you want to follow Xingyao's updates,

153
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:55,780
you can follow Star River Music.

154
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,300
We and Tiantian Studio

155
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:58,740
will also have deeper collaboration.

156
00:10:58,980 --> 00:11:00,420
Please stay tuned.

157
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:11,700
Xiao Yao,

158
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:12,860
do you know?

159
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,460
Today on stage,

160
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:16,180
you shone brilliantly.

161
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,420
I am truly proud of you.

162
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,260
What if we get photographed?

163
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:10,100
I don't care.

164
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:18,180
From the day I understood my own heart,

165
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,900
I never planned to hide you away.

166
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,380
So don't you care either, okay?

167
00:12:23,420 --> 00:12:24,580
As long as you're by my side,

168
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:26,340
I don't care about anything.

169
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:58,780
That trophy —

170
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,340
it's the first award I got for original work.

171
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:05,420
Finally I can make something decent.

172
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:15,620
I hope

173
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:19,060
that in the future, your trophies and mine will be placed together.

174
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:21,980
Do you think I can do it?

175
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:24,820
Xiao Yao,

176
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:28,100
why don't you move in with me?

177
00:13:33,980 --> 00:13:36,940
Seeing you sing on stage today,

178
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:40,060
I suddenly became selfish.

179
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:42,900
Such a beautiful Xiao Yao —

180
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:45,420
I want her right now.

181
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:50,900
But I don't want to right now.

182
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:30,820
The media situation is basically under control.

183
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:33,540
The press release direction focuses on Xingyao's professional ability

184
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:34,700
and stage breakthrough.

185
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,860
We try to avoid her emotional issues.

186
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:38,500
As for the part about her personal experience,

187
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,220
we didn't suppress the heat or control the comments.

188
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:41,140
I think

189
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:43,180
this is probably what Xingyao wants.

190
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:45,460
You've done very well.

191
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:46,580
Also,

192
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:47,300
regarding Wang Daqiang,

193
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:49,980
the lawyer has compiled all the evidence

194
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,580
and submitted it to the police.

195
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:53,980
I will follow up on the case filing and progress.

196
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:55,260
Xiu Jie,

197
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,460
thank you for helping Xiao Yao gather evidence.

198
00:15:57,740 --> 00:15:58,940
This is what I should do.

199
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:17,500
Wang Rui has already posted an apology video.

200
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:18,780
Isn't that right?

201
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:20,020
Blacklist?

202
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:29,380
Didn't Wang Rui already apologize?

203
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:31,540
An apology

204
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:33,700
is only the minimum compensation

205
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:35,740
to you, psychologically and morally.

206
00:16:47,500 --> 00:16:48,900
I have never believed

207
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:51,940
that a person's repentance, born under the pressure

208
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:53,540
of disadvantage and fear,

209
00:16:53,860 --> 00:16:55,420
can change their nature.

210
00:16:58,500 --> 00:16:59,620
If a simple "sorry"

211
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:01,620
could solve all problems,

212
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,220
that would be encouraging everyone

213
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:05,500
to test boundaries even more recklessly next time.

214
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:15,380
Only by making them pay a truly painful price

215
00:17:15,820 --> 00:17:17,020
will they remember

216
00:17:18,060 --> 00:17:19,980
what exactly one must bear for trampling on others.

217
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:22,220
Xiao Yao,

218
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:24,940
precisely because of your kindness,

219
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:27,020
that's why I have to push you

220
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,740
to be even more relentless,

221
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:31,820
sharper, even more domineering.

222
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,900
I know you're doing this to protect me.

223
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:26,060
I was impulsive back then.

224
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:32,540
That's good.

225
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:52,180
What I've preserved

226
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:54,180
is our past.

227
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,660
And what you've pieced together

228
00:18:57,220 --> 00:18:59,020
is our different future.
